NAME
    perl-module-examples - Tool for creating examples from Perl module POD
    documentation.

SYNOPSIS
     perl-module-examples [-d] [-h] [--version]

DESCRIPTION
    Tool to create examples/ directory in Perl distribution, which is
    generated by Pod::Example from *.pm modules.

ARGUMENTS
    *       "-d"

            Turn on debug mode.

    *       "-h"

            Print help.

    *       "--version"

            Print version of script.

EXAMPLE
     perl-module-examples -h

REPOSITORY
    <https://github.com/michal-josef-spacek/App-Perl-Module-Examples>

